        "title": "Confusion about Thread",
        "body": "<p>We can create a reference of an interface but not object. But how can we pass new Runnable() to the Thread constructor. As per as my knowledge is concert new Class_Name() is object.<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>Thread t = new Thread(new Runnable(){});\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
